



Running Tests
-------------

running single tests

1) You will need XML Calabash to run tests, download and install from http://xmlcalabash.com

2) edit src/tests/config.xml to reflect your setup

3) run test.xpl

  /usr/local/bin/calabash -isource=config.xml -oresult=result/report.xml test.xpl

( TBD ) running test suite

  bin/test.sh



